{"tid":1206214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【0957】夏愨道 示威者已佔領全部六線行車道","createTime":"2019-06-12T01:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T02:43:04.000Z","uid":52609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"586e34b9459a295ab98881339fcc65382901a807","tid":1206214,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"【0957】夏愨道 示威者已佔領全部六線行車道<br />\n【0943】添華道 發射催淚水劑<br />\n【0930】海富中心外 設有急救站<br />\n【0925】公務員可使用東翼二樓職員入口進出政府總部<br />\n【0922】金鐘站恢復上落客，包括港島、荃灣、南港島線"},{"pid":"fba2221c0a3643367cc148ee55c690ca04afac3d","tid":1206214,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:59:45.000Z","msg":"只佔夏愨道有咩用，人多就要郁"},{"pid":"98a8e5d0e76c0cb96ba02790f9ff7579a9260e27","tid":1206214,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"__ __ __ __ , __ __ __ __ !"},{"pid":"c4cb4ca712163e860860633e938ad987622480ea","tid":1206214,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b830a952de26943c4f9666083ba7391a032222b5","tid":1206214,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462236-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462236-20190612.htm&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=218b2f19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462236-20190612.htm&h=7633e886\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462236-20190612.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者進佔特首辦外  與警員對峙  警方舉紅旗警告</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462236_1_L_20190612090011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462236_1_L_20190612090011.jpg&h=8b79f872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會今日恢復二讀辯論《逃犯條例》修訂草案，早上8時前，大批示威者突然衝出龍和道，用大量鐵馬及水馬佔據路面，堵塞東西行車線，附近一帶交通受影響，車輛要調頭離開，又呼籲在立法會外聚集的市民到來；有示威者則在特首辦外與警員對峙。<br />\n<br />\n示威者手挽手向前行，部分人叫口號，亦有人拍打警車，期間落起雨。大批防暴警員佈防，警方其後舉起紅旗，警告示威者不得越過封鎖線。"},{"pid":"65a5b09de91ba979ede63e71a2acf42945fdf660","tid":1206214,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"而家係咪反包圍？<br />\n<br />\n(第三十五條 中華人民共和國公民有言論、出版、集會、結社、游行、示威的自由。)"}]}